<HEADLINE> Jordan's Stock Market Closed Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, May 5 (Xinhua) -- Volume of trading for both organized
and parallel markets in Amman Financial Market (AFM), Jordan's
sole stock market, on Tuesday was 1,059,013 Jordanian dinars
(about 1,495,781 U.S. dollars), or some 52 percent lower from that
of Monday.
