for they did not get what they thought they should have got.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, citizens in the capital Monrovia are sympathized
with the retired soldiers as underpayment is not only the problem
with the retired soldiers, but also one with the civil service,
the report said.
</P>
<P>
Troops of the west African peace keeping force ECOMOG have
sealed off that area, it said, without indicating whether or not
the crisis has been solved by now. 
