Trade Organization (WTO), accusing Greek television channels of
regularly broadcasting American programs and films without paying
U.S. copyright holders.
</P>
<P>
Greece and the U.S. will now have 60 days to negotiate a
settlement before a WTO hearing panel is appointed. 
