experts from Argentina to assist land reform and empowerment of
the country's indigenous small-scale farmers to its boost
agricultural production.
</P>
<P>
Zimbabwean Minister of State in the Presidential office,
Cephas Msipa said Wednesday that Zimbabwe had a lot to learn from
Argentina's success story, especially in the agricultural sector.
</P>
<P>
