of the Southern African Development Community engaged in economic
reforms, a government spokesman has said.
</P>
<P>
The symposium was organized by the argentinian embassy here
and was attended by government representatives from eight
countries from the SADC: Angola, Lesotho, Malawi, Mozambique,
Namibia, South Africa, Zambia and Zimbabwe. 
