<TEXT>
<P>
NANJING, May 6 (Xinhua) -- An inauguration ceremony for an
educational exchange center jointly set up by Chinese and Australian
schools was held today in this capital of east China's Jiangsu
Province.
</P>
<P>
The center was jointly launched by a middle school affiliated
to Nanjing Teachers' University and Australia's renowned Caulfield
Grammar School.
</P>
