<HEADLINE> University Students Keen on Deng Xiaoping Theory </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEFEI, May 6 (Xinhua) -- Students at the Chinese University of
Science and Technology in Hefei, capital of east China's Anhui
Province, are keen on the study of Deng Xiaoping Theory.
</P>
<P>
To provide students with a systematic knowledge about Deng
Xiaoping Theory, the university has set up an institute on the
subject.
</P>
<P>
In recent years the university has opened a series of courses
and lectures about Marxism-Leninism, the Constitution of the
Communist Party of China (CPC) and Deng Xiaoping Theory.
</P>
<P>
More than 1,000 students have formed 80 groups to study the
courses or attend lectures, 70 percent more than seven years ago.
</P>
<P>
To date, students have written more than 50 papers about their
understanding and research on Deng Xiaoping Theory, and 500 of
them have applied for CPC membership. 
