Colombian "Cartel de Cali," Ugarte said.
</P>
<P>
He said the police started preparatory investigation for
Monday's operation as early as 1992, when a motorboat was detained
on the Guantanamo sea shore with a Chilean crew and five tons of
cocaine on board. 
