said on Monday that she felt her career was nearing its end and
had given up hope of being fit to play at the French Open, which
started on May 25 in Paris.
</P>
<P>
Graf has been out of action since suffering a leg injury in
California in March. She had only just returned from a nine-month
lay-off following knee surgery. 
