<HEADLINE> New Trade Center Slated for Guangdong </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, May 6 (Xinhua) -- China's largest trade center
for tourism commodities will be established in Jiangmen City,
Guangdong Province.
</P>
<P>
The Jiangmen International Tourism Hotel Commodity Trade Center
will be jointly funded by the Jiangmen city government, the
Jiangmen Yihua Industrial Development Company and the China
Tourism Newspaper.
</P>
